<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html lang="en" xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head>
  <title>Wikispaces - Site Maintenance</title>
  <meta content="text/html;charset=utf-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  <style type="text/css">
body {
  font-family: verdana,arial,sans-serif;
  font-size: 83%;
  background-color: #FFF;
}
#container {
  background: #FFF;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  width: 760px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
}
#head {
  margin: 24px auto;
  text-align: center;
}
#head h1 {
  font-family: 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', sans-serif;
  font-size: 40px;
  font-weight: normal;
  text-shadow: #AAA 0px 1px 1px;
  color: #074F16;
}
#head h1 span {
  padding: 10px 0px 0px 4px;
}
#box {
  text-align: center;
  width: 500px;
  background-color: #EFFFE9;
  padding: 16px;
  margin: auto;
  border: 1px solid #DDD;
  -moz-border-radius: 8px;
  -webkit-border-top-left-radius: 8px;
  -webkit-border-top-right-radius: 8px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  -webkit-box-shadow: 4px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  -moz-box-shadow: 4px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  box-shadow: 4px 4px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  filter:progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.dropshadow(OffX=4, OffY=4, Color='gray'); /* IE */
  -ms-filter:"progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.dropshadow(OffX=4, OffY=4, Color='gray')"; /* IE8 */
}
h1 {
  color: #001;
  margin: .5em 0;
  font-size: 140%;
}
p {
  margin: 1em 0;
  text-align: left;
}
p.right {
  text-align: right;
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="container">

<div id="head">
  <h1>
  <!-- /i/logo-34x40.png -->
  <img width="34" height="40" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="" title="" /><span>Wikispaces</span></h1>
</div>

<div id="box">
<h1>Be Back Soon!</h1>
<p>Wikispaces is currently offline for maintenance.  You can find out up-to-the-minute details at our <a href="http://status.wikispaces.com/">off-site status page</a>.</p>
<p>Thanks for your patience - and rest assured that we are hard at work bringing the site back as quickly as possible.</p>
<p class="right">- James and the Wikispaces Team<br /><a href="mailto:help@wikispaces.com">help@wikispaces.com</a></p>
</div>

</div>
